title: Population of Luxembourg 2019 , by age
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of inhabitants. In total the number of data points it has is 20.
In general Number of inhabitants has fallen over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 5-9_years and 50-54_years.
The highest Number of inhabitants, of value 48111.0 was reached at Year 35-39_years
The lowest Number of inhabitants, of value 766.0 was reported at Year 95_years_and_older
